question: Give me the museums and planetariums with tickets priced at $15.
sql_query1:
SELECT Venue.name 
FROM Venue
WHERE (Venue.educationalVenue = "Museum" OR Venue.educationalVenue = "Planetarium") AND Venue.ticketPrice = "$15"
sql_query2:
SELECT Venue.name 
FROM Venue
WHERE Venue.educationalVenue = "Museum" OR Venue.educationalVenue = "Planetarium" AND Venue.ticketPrice = "$15"
interpretation1: What museums have tickets priced at $15 and what planetariums have the same price?
interpretation2: Provide a list of all museums and also provide a list of planetariums with tickets priced at $15.
